{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_131","type":"agent_message","text":"Completed the full research execution.\n\nMain result: neural-symbolic composition worked strongly on the AddMNIST OOD test. With 5,000 weak pair labels, `symbolic_sum` reached 82.5% high-plus-high OOD accuracy, while the direct CNN reached 0.3%. On sums 14-18 that never appeared as training labels, `symbolic_sum` reached 80.6%; direct CNN reached 0.0%. The planned anchor-posterior variant did not beat the simpler symbolic likelihood baseline, which is documented as a negative ablation result.\n\nPrimary deliverables:\n- [REPORT.md](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/REPORT.md)\n- [README.md](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/README.md)\n- [planning.md](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/planning.md)\n- [src/addmnist_experiment.py](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/src/addmnist_experiment.py)\n- [src/analyze_results.py](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/src/analyze_results.py)\n\nOutputs are in [results/addmnist](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/results/addmnist) and figures are in [figures](/workspaces/neural-symbolic-ai-2f28-codex/figures).\n\nValidation passed:\n- Isolated `.venv` used; dependencies tracked in `pyproject.toml`.\n- GPU detected and used: NVIDIA RTX A6000 on `cuda:0`.\n- `python -m py_compile src/addmnist_experiment.py src/analyze_results.py` passed.\n- Same-seed reproducibility check produced identical metrics and predictions.\n- Final run produced 66 metric rows and 192,000 per-example predictions."}}
